### Describe the bug

Is it really fixed here https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/26661 ? 
I am using oidc-client and followed this [guide](https://quarkus.io/guides/security-openid-connect-client-reference) for config. I am hitting head for many hours without knowing where is error and  why NPE. I don't know why there is no explicit message.

